WEBVTT

00:06.206 --> 00:08.675
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:08.709 --> 00:10.444
HOW ABOUT
MOVING INTO MY HOUSE?

00:10.477 --> 00:12.212
THERE'S PLENTY OF ROOM
FOR THE BOYS.

00:12.246 --> 00:13.647
DID YOU JUST ASK ME
TO LIVE WITH YOU?

00:13.680 --> 00:14.748
WE'RE GOING TO DENMARK.

00:14.781 --> 00:17.651
THE MEXICAN MAFIA'S
NOT GONNA FIND US IN COPENHAGEN.

00:17.684 --> 00:19.319
MR. SANDUSKY?
I NEED SOME POT.

00:19.353 --> 00:21.688
HOW MUCH CAN YOU SPEND?
FOUR GRAND.

00:21.722 --> 00:23.557
GET IN,
WE'LL SETTLE UP.

00:23.590 --> 00:25.459
WOW, TO BE YOU!

00:27.060 --> 00:28.562
WHAT KIND OF BUSINESS
YOU GOT?

00:28.595 --> 00:29.596
MEDICAL MARIJUANA.

00:29.630 --> 00:31.565
WE'RE IN BUSINESS, <i>PARTNER.</i>

00:31.598 --> 00:32.766
PARTNER.
PARTNERS.

00:32.799 --> 00:33.767
FAGGOTS.

00:33.800 --> 00:37.971
$186,437.96.

00:38.005 --> 00:40.374
YOU GO OUT WITH ME, AND I'LL
GET YOU INTO THAT ACCOUNT.

00:40.407 --> 00:43.443
ONLY IT HAS TO BE AS JUDAH.
YOU'RE JUDAH, AND I'M ME.

00:43.477 --> 00:45.479
WELL, THERE'S NOTHING
WEIRD ABOUT THAT.

00:45.512 --> 00:48.382
YOU REMEMBER SUCIO.
HE WILL WATCH YOU NOW.

00:48.415 --> 00:51.151
WHERE IS SUCIO?
Nancy: HE'S MISSING.
THERE WAS BLOOD.

00:51.185 --> 00:54.321
YOU HAVE TO CHOOSE, NANCY.
WHO'S IT GONNA BE?

00:54.354 --> 00:56.990
I'M NOT READY TO BE FUCKING ZEN
ABOUT WHO LIVES OR DIES.

00:57.024 --> 01:00.327
WE CHOSE THIS LIFE FOR YOU,
FOR ME, FOR OUR SON.

01:00.360 --> 01:04.631
THERE IS NOTHING I WILL NOT DO
TO PROTECT THAT LIFE.

01:06.567 --> 01:09.570
[ BIRD SQUAWKS ]

01:22.516 --> 01:23.483
[ SIGHS ]

01:23.517 --> 01:25.385
CAN YOU SMELL THAT?

01:25.419 --> 01:27.020
YOU KNOW THE ONE THING
ABOUT WOMEN

01:27.054 --> 01:28.488
THAT TERRIFIES ME
ABOVE EVERYTHING?

01:28.522 --> 01:29.423
HOW CAN SHE EAT THAT?

01:29.456 --> 01:32.659
THE FACT THAT YOUR PERIODS
SYNC UP.

01:32.693 --> 01:34.361
IT'S NOT EVEN FOOD.

01:34.394 --> 01:36.330
IT'S JUST NITRATES
AND FILLERS AND...

01:36.363 --> 01:38.131
IT'S SO FREAKY
AND WOLFISH.

01:38.165 --> 01:39.233
WHAT'S A FILLER?

01:39.266 --> 01:41.101
I BET YOU'RE
AN ALPHA SHE‐WOLF, NANCE.

01:41.134 --> 01:44.104
I BET ALL WOMEN IN YOUR ORBIT
SNAP TO YOUR CYCLE.

01:44.137 --> 01:45.973
IT'S TERRIFYING.
EXCUSE ME.

01:46.006 --> 01:47.574
NOT IN THE HABIT
OF BUTTING IN,

01:47.608 --> 01:50.244
BUT THOSE CAN'T BE THE BEST
FOR YOUR BABY.

01:50.277 --> 01:53.881
WELL, IT'S NOT A BABY YET,
AND I'M NOT KEEPING IT.

01:53.914 --> 01:56.049
AH, AN ABOBO, HUH?
HOOVERTOWN?

01:56.083 --> 01:58.519
WE USED TO CALL IT
"GOING TO VAN NUYS."

01:58.552 --> 01:59.453
ANDY.

01:59.486 --> 02:00.954
'CAUSE THE PLACE WE'D GO
WAS IN VAN NUYS.

02:00.988 --> 02:02.356
SORRY
TO HAVE BOTHERED YOU.

02:02.389 --> 02:04.525
I'VE GONE TO VAN NUYS
FIVE TIMES. IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

02:04.558 --> 02:05.526
UH, FOR <i>ME.</i>

02:05.559 --> 02:08.996
THE LADIES TENDED TO...
GET A LITTLE WEEPY.

02:09.029 --> 02:10.297
EXCEPT FOR DEIRDRE.

02:10.330 --> 02:13.667
BUT I FOUND OUT LATER
SHE HAD ASPERGER'S.

02:13.700 --> 02:14.868
FIVE?

02:14.902 --> 02:17.604
MY POINT IS THIS...

02:17.638 --> 02:20.607
SCIENCE.

02:20.641 --> 02:22.843
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
SINCE THE FIRST ULTRASOUND.

02:22.876 --> 02:24.044
HOW ARE YOU?

02:24.077 --> 02:26.446
I'VE BEEN NAUSEOUS.
IT'S MY SENSE OF SMELL.

02:26.480 --> 02:27.981
BIONIC, HUH?

02:28.015 --> 02:29.583
I COULD BE
A SUPERHERO.

02:29.616 --> 02:32.619
ONE OF THE MIRACULOUS
WEIRDNESSES OF PREGNANCY.

02:32.653 --> 02:34.488
MOSTLY I SMELL ‐‐

02:34.521 --> 02:36.490
AH ‐‐

02:36.523 --> 02:37.457
THE BAD THINGS.

02:37.491 --> 02:39.293
I'M SURROUNDED BY MEN.

02:39.326 --> 02:41.962
I BREATHE THROUGH MY MOUTH
SO MUCH, MY LIPS CHAP.

02:41.995 --> 02:42.996
I'M FINE, REALLY.

02:43.030 --> 02:44.898
SO, YOU DO ABORTIONS,
TOO, RIGHT?

02:44.932 --> 02:46.066
YES.

02:46.099 --> 02:47.334
SO, UH,
HOW LATE IS TOO LATE?

02:47.367 --> 02:49.036
WELL, YOU STILL
HAVE SOME TIME.

02:49.069 --> 02:51.471
IS THIS SOMETHING
YOU'RE SERIOUSLY CONSIDERING?

02:51.505 --> 02:53.240
I DON'T KNOW.

02:53.273 --> 02:55.008
NO.

02:55.042 --> 02:56.677
I'LL THINK ABOUT IT.

02:56.710 --> 02:58.879
WELL,
EVERYTHING LOOKS FINE.

02:58.912 --> 03:01.315
TRY TO FIND AN OASIS.

03:01.348 --> 03:03.383
CREATE ONE
IF YOU HAVE TO.

03:03.417 --> 03:06.420
AND I WOULD SURROUND MYSELF
WITH NICE SMELLS.

03:06.453 --> 03:08.555
WHAT, LIKE FLOWERS?

03:08.589 --> 03:09.957
I WAS THINKING PANCAKES.

03:09.990 --> 03:10.958
[ LAUGHS ]

03:10.991 --> 03:13.260
BUT FLOWERS, TOO, YES.
HERBS, MAYBE.

03:13.293 --> 03:15.729
WOULD YOU LIKE ME TO MAKE YOU
ANOTHER APPOINTMENT?

03:15.762 --> 03:17.497
FOR A FOLLOW‐UP?

03:17.531 --> 03:19.566
FOR WHATEVER YOU DECIDE.

03:19.600 --> 03:20.267
[ SIGHS ]

03:20.300 --> 03:22.936
[ HARD‐ROCK MUSIC PLAYING ]

03:22.970 --> 03:25.372
FUCKING COCKBREATH ASSHOLE!

03:25.405 --> 03:30.110
DICKHEAD!
SHITBRAIN! MAN‐CUNT!

03:35.315 --> 03:37.217
[ MUSIC STOPS,
CAR ALARM BLARING IN DISTANCE ]

03:37.251 --> 03:39.219
ANGRY,
RICH WHITE CHILDREN.

03:39.253 --> 03:42.189
YOU'RE RICH AND WHITE.
WHY SO ANGRY?

03:42.222 --> 03:44.024
SHANE GOT JACKED
FOR HIS WEED.

03:44.057 --> 03:45.893
I JUST LIKE
SEEING SHIT BREAK.

03:45.926 --> 03:47.394
JACKED?

03:47.427 --> 03:49.830
RIPPED OFF.
MUCH POT, NO PAY.

03:49.863 --> 03:51.265
BY HIS ENGLISH TEACHER.

03:51.298 --> 03:55.736
SO, WHAT YOU
GOING TO DO ABOUT IT?

04:00.174 --> 04:02.142
POTTING SOIL...
OVERPOPULATION...

04:02.176 --> 04:03.544
BASIL...
HIVE COLLAPSE...

04:03.577 --> 04:06.513
LAVENDER...
CREDIT‐DEFAULT SWAPS,
SOMALI PIRATES...

04:06.547 --> 04:08.882
WHAT'S THIS ONE?
NORTH KOREAN NUKES...

04:08.916 --> 04:10.284
LOVAGE ‐‐
HERB LOVAGE...

04:10.317 --> 04:13.387
MEXICAN DRUG‐LORD
GANGSTER‐POLITICIANS...
LOVAGE...

04:13.420 --> 04:15.622
"AMERICAN IDOL."
GOLDEN OREGANO...

04:15.656 --> 04:17.191
DID YOU KNOW
THAT THIS BABY

04:17.224 --> 04:19.760
HAS A ONE‐IN‐FIVE CHANCE
OF BEING AUTISTIC?

04:19.793 --> 04:21.128
WHY DID I BUY MARJORAM?

04:21.161 --> 04:22.462
AND I'M NOT TALKING
THE FUN,

04:22.496 --> 04:24.498
CARD‐COUNTING SAVANT KIND,
EITHER.

04:24.531 --> 04:29.303
I'M TALKING ZOMBIE‐EYES,
SOOTHE‐ROCKING, BEHELMETED.

04:29.336 --> 04:31.038
WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF CORIANDER?

04:31.071 --> 04:32.272
I THINK NOTHING
OF CORIANDER!

04:32.306 --> 04:34.441
ALTHOUGH,
IT'S NICE IN A CURRY.

04:34.474 --> 04:36.944
YOU HAVE TO GET RID
OF THIS BABY.

04:36.977 --> 04:37.978
NO, I DON'T.

04:38.011 --> 04:39.079
FLUSH IT.

04:39.112 --> 04:42.382
LISTEN,
I'M COMING INTO SOME MONEY.

04:42.416 --> 04:46.153
WE'LL RUN,
GET A FRESH START.

04:46.186 --> 04:49.022
THESE ARE VERY DARK WATERS
YOU'RE SWIMMING IN,

04:49.056 --> 04:51.925
EVEN FOR YOU.

04:51.959 --> 04:53.193
[ SIGHS ]

04:53.227 --> 04:55.863
I JUST ‐‐ WHAT ARE YOU DOING
WITH ALL THIS STUFF?

04:55.896 --> 04:57.264
I'M GONNA PLANT THINGS,

04:57.297 --> 04:59.800
AND THEY'LL BLOOM AND FLOURISH
AND SMELL GOOD AND MAYBE...

04:59.833 --> 05:01.168
[ SIGHS ]

05:01.201 --> 05:05.005
...THE MOODS WILL RISE
AND THE DARK WATERS WILL CLEAR.

05:05.038 --> 05:07.708
MONEY ‐‐ BRICKS OF IT,
WRAPPED IN THOSE ‐‐
[ Singsong voice ]
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

05:07.741 --> 05:09.343
HEY, I DON'T WANT
TO TELL YOU.
BLAH, BLAH, BLAH, BLAH.

05:09.376 --> 05:11.411
YOU KNOW GOPHERS AND BUNNIES ARE
GONNA EAT YOUR PLANTS, RIGHT?

05:11.445 --> 05:12.846
I'LL BUILD A FENCE.

05:12.880 --> 05:15.949
YEAH, WELL, MAYBE THE GOPHER'S
ALREADY INSIDE, HUH?
BLAH, BLAH, BLAH.

05:15.983 --> 05:17.751
JUST WAITING AND GROWING...
HEY, SHUT UP!

05:17.784 --> 05:21.188
...SUCKING THE NUTRIENTS
FROM YOUR SOIL.
SHUT UP!

05:21.221 --> 05:23.557
YOU GOT TO ABORT
THAT GOPHER, NANCE!

05:27.961 --> 05:29.329
HOW'S THE SAMPLE?

05:29.363 --> 05:31.665
SUCKS ‐‐
TOTAL DITCH WEED.

05:31.698 --> 05:34.101
WE ONLY HAVE THREE GOOD STRAINS,
AND I'M OUT OF CONTACTS.

05:34.134 --> 05:35.068
WE'RE FUCKED.

05:35.102 --> 05:36.837
C.P.:
WELL, THAT IS A PICKLE.

05:36.870 --> 05:39.673
YOU SHOULD GO
SEE THE WIZARD.

05:39.706 --> 05:41.341
WHO?

05:41.375 --> 05:42.376
BUDDY OF MINE
FROM HIGH SCHOOL,

05:42.409 --> 05:43.944
DROPPED OUT,
WENT INTO REAL ESTATE,

05:43.977 --> 05:45.212
MARKET TANKED,
SO NOW HE'S A POT AGENT.

05:45.245 --> 05:46.813
POT GROWERS HAVE AGENTS?

05:46.847 --> 05:47.981
OH, SURE.

05:48.015 --> 05:50.284
GROWERS ARE USUALLY
TOO STONED TO DO MATH.

05:50.317 --> 05:52.319
YEAH, THAT'S TRUE.
MATH IS HARD.

05:52.352 --> 05:53.787
I'LL SET UP A MEETING
FOR YOU, SI.

05:53.820 --> 05:55.055
OH, OH!
ME TOO! ME TOO!

05:55.088 --> 05:57.824
I WANT THE HOOKUP
FOR THE MEETING AND THE BUYING.

05:57.858 --> 05:59.293
NEGOTIATIONS CAN BE TRICKY,
DOUG.

05:59.326 --> 06:01.995
FUCK OFF!
I'M A MASTER NEGOTIATOR.

06:02.029 --> 06:03.530
BESIDES,
YOU CAN'T NEGOTIATE.

06:03.564 --> 06:05.599
NO ONE'S GONNA
TAKE A BLOND MAN SERIOUSLY.

06:08.335 --> 06:09.102
OW!

06:09.136 --> 06:11.572
HOOKED! HOOKED! HOOKED!

06:29.623 --> 06:32.526
[ CLATTERING, LOUD THUD ]

06:32.559 --> 06:34.428
HELLO?

06:34.461 --> 06:35.896
W‐WHO'S THERE?

06:35.929 --> 06:37.264
I HAVE A GUN!

06:37.297 --> 06:38.599
Celia: DON'T SHOOT!
IT'S ME.

06:40.767 --> 06:42.703
[ SIGHS ]

06:42.736 --> 06:44.238
LIAR ‐‐
YOU DON'T HAVE A GUN.

06:44.271 --> 06:46.874
YOU'RE SQUATTING
IN MY GARAGE?!

06:46.907 --> 06:48.909
I HAVE NOWHERE TO GO.

06:48.942 --> 06:50.143
[ SIGHS ]

06:50.177 --> 06:53.213
MY FAMILY IS IN RUINS ‐‐
SHARDS, NANCY.

06:53.247 --> 06:56.617
THEY LEFT ME TO ROT
IN MEXICO.

06:56.650 --> 06:57.751
GET OUT OF MY LIFE!

06:57.784 --> 06:59.553
CANCER...

06:59.586 --> 07:01.522
LOSS OF STATION...

07:01.555 --> 07:03.223
LOSS OF...TOOTH.

07:03.257 --> 07:05.559
YOU THREW AWAY MY TOOTH.

07:05.592 --> 07:06.460
GET OUT OF MY LIFE.

07:06.493 --> 07:09.196
I JUST LOSE AND LOSE
AND LOSE AND LOSE,

07:09.229 --> 07:10.831
AND YOU HAVE EVERYTHING.

07:10.864 --> 07:12.533
Get out of my life.

07:12.566 --> 07:14.301
AND NOW A BABY.

07:14.334 --> 07:16.470
A MEXICAN BABY,
BUT STILL.

07:16.503 --> 07:22.176
SO ALLOW ME THIS TINY,
LITTLE, PATHETIC CRUMB ‐‐

07:22.209 --> 07:24.811
TO STAY IN YOUR GARAGE
WHILE I FIGURE OUT

07:24.845 --> 07:27.247
WHAT THE FUCK I'M DOING
WITH MY LIFE!

07:27.281 --> 07:28.715
ALBATROSS.

07:28.749 --> 07:30.751
MY OWN PERSONAL
CINDER BLOCK.

07:32.719 --> 07:33.687
TWO DAYS.

07:33.720 --> 07:36.557
I DON'T WANT TO SEE YOU.

07:37.424 --> 07:39.326
THANK YOU, NANCY.

07:40.460 --> 07:44.164
CAN I HAVE MY OLD JOB BACK
AT THE MATERNITY STORE?

07:50.137 --> 07:53.340
[ JAZZ MUSIC PLAYING,
THEREMIN SQUEALING ]

08:00.881 --> 08:03.250
FUCK!

08:03.283 --> 08:04.318
BOTWIN?

08:04.351 --> 08:05.986
THAT'S RIGHT.
IT'S BOTWIN, MOTHERFUCKER.

08:06.019 --> 08:07.688
AND HODES, JERK.

08:08.956 --> 08:10.490
DON'T MESS WITH HER.
SHE'S LOCO.

08:10.524 --> 08:11.558
I REALLY AM.

08:11.592 --> 08:13.493
GET THE FUCK OUT OF HERE
BEFORE I KICK YOUR NARDS IN,

08:13.527 --> 08:16.797
YOU LITTLE COCK GOBLIN,
WITH YOUR FAKE GUN.

08:16.830 --> 08:18.165
TAKE NERD‐GIRL
WITH YOU.

08:18.198 --> 08:20.567
YOUR USUAL SIDEKICKS
ARE MUCH HOTTER.

08:20.601 --> 08:21.535
AAH!

08:21.568 --> 08:23.103
[ BIRD SQUAWKS ]

08:23.136 --> 08:25.706
YOU KNOW THAT LESSON YOU TAUGHT
ON POINT OF VIEW IN FICTION?

08:25.739 --> 08:28.075
IT WAS REALLY HELPFUL,
MR. S.

08:28.108 --> 08:29.276
I THINK I GET IT NOW.

08:29.309 --> 08:32.212
TO YOU, I'M JUST SOME DUMB KID
YOU CAN RIP OFF.

08:32.246 --> 08:34.248
WELL,
FROM MY PERSPECTIVE,

08:34.281 --> 08:37.251
YOU'RE THAT TITANIC LOSER
OF A TEACHER I ONCE HAD

08:37.284 --> 08:40.420
WHO JACKED
THE WRONG KID.

08:42.055 --> 08:43.323
UNFORTUNATELY,

08:43.357 --> 08:45.792
YOU'RE ALSO NOW PART
OF OUR FRIEND IGNACIO'S STORY.

08:45.826 --> 08:50.764
AND YOUR CHAPTER
IS VERY, VERY SHORT.

08:50.797 --> 08:53.767
HERE. IT'S ALL THERE.
TAKE IT.

08:53.800 --> 08:58.005
I DIDN'T ASK YOUR PERMISSION,
YOU FAUX‐ADULT! YOU SKID MARK!

08:58.038 --> 09:00.174
YOUR APARTMENT
MAKES ME SAD.

09:02.409 --> 09:05.646
TAKE SOMETHING ELSE ‐‐
FOR PENALTY.

09:05.679 --> 09:07.014
OKAY.

09:07.047 --> 09:08.982
UM, THE RAY‐BANS.

09:09.850 --> 09:11.752
AND THE ROLLERBLADES.

09:11.785 --> 09:14.321
IS THAT A ZUNE?
TAKE THAT.

09:15.789 --> 09:17.491
UM...

09:17.524 --> 09:18.859
NOT MY AXE!

09:18.892 --> 09:20.861
OKAY, NOW THAT
YOU CALLED IT YOUR AXE,

09:20.894 --> 09:22.029
I'M FOR SURE TAKING IT.

09:22.062 --> 09:24.765
NOW SHOOT HIM
IN THE LEG.

09:24.798 --> 09:26.767
[ BIRD SQUAWKS ]

09:26.800 --> 09:28.302
AAH!

09:28.335 --> 09:29.436
NOT THE BIRD!

09:29.469 --> 09:31.572
[ Voice breaking ]
I MEANT THE MAN!

09:32.506 --> 09:34.708
POOR LITTLE BIRDIE.

09:34.741 --> 09:37.311
G‐G‐GO, GO!
GO, GO!

09:37.344 --> 09:40.314
Wizard: AGING GOOFBALL ‐‐
CAREER IN THE SHIT TANK.

09:40.347 --> 09:43.283
MIDDLE‐CLASS KID ‐‐ LOST,
NOT SMART ENOUGH FOR ACADEMICS,

09:43.317 --> 09:46.019
NOT TALENTED ENOUGH
FOR SPORTS.

09:46.053 --> 09:47.321
MY POINT ‐‐

09:47.354 --> 09:51.225
YOU TWO DON'T STRIKE ME
AS A PARTICULARLY SERIOUS DUO.

09:51.258 --> 09:52.526
OH, WE ARE SERIOUS,
BRO.

09:52.559 --> 09:55.062
SERIOUS AS ASS CANCER,
SERIOUS AS NAGASAKI,

09:55.095 --> 09:56.763
SERIOUS
AS A SEAN PENN MOVIE.

09:56.797 --> 09:59.399
LOOK, WE'VE GOT
A SOLID BUSINESS PLAN,

09:59.433 --> 10:01.301
A COMMUNITY ITCHING
FOR LEGAL PRODUCT,

10:01.335 --> 10:03.604
AND YOUR BUDDY C. P. ‐‐
HE'S GOT OUR BACK.

10:03.637 --> 10:04.905
C.P.'s
FUNCTIONALLY RETARDED.

10:04.938 --> 10:06.473
THE ONLY REASON
I USED TO HANG OUT WITH HIM

10:06.507 --> 10:08.242
IS 'CAUSE HIS STEPMOM
HAD JELL‐O POPS

10:08.275 --> 10:10.811
AND HIS LITTLE SISTER
LET ME FINGER‐BANG HER
IN THE POOL HOUSE.

10:10.844 --> 10:13.447
FUCKING LOVED
PUDDING POPS.

10:13.480 --> 10:15.549
WHY DON'T THEY MAKE THOSE
ANYMORE?

10:15.582 --> 10:16.450
KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

10:16.483 --> 10:18.552
I STOCK EVERYTHING
IN YOUR DISPENSARY.

10:19.553 --> 10:20.921
AND I MEAN <i>EVERYTHING.</i>

10:20.954 --> 10:22.723
GREAT. PERFECT.

10:22.756 --> 10:24.191
WE'RE IN.

10:24.224 --> 10:25.125
OKAY.

10:25.158 --> 10:28.428
LET'S DO THE PAPERWORK.

10:28.462 --> 10:31.532
UH, SO, WE'LL START WITH
THE SMALL‐MARKET CONTRACTS...

10:31.565 --> 10:32.966
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

10:33.000 --> 10:34.434
...ADDING
THE $75 DELIVERY FEE...

10:34.468 --> 10:36.136
WHOA, WHOA, THERE.
DELIVERY FEE?

10:36.170 --> 10:37.337
WE HAVE TO PAY
OUR DRIVERS.

10:37.371 --> 10:39.339
YOU HAVE TO PAY
YOUR DRIVERS.
DOUG ‐‐

10:39.373 --> 10:41.675
LET ME NEGOTIATE.
THIS IS WHAT I DO.

10:41.708 --> 10:43.477
NO DEAL, WIZARD.

10:43.510 --> 10:47.648
FUCK YOU AND YOUR
BULLSHIT CHARGES IN THE BUTT.

10:47.681 --> 10:49.316
IT'S A STANDARD FEE.

10:49.349 --> 10:51.351
OKAY,
HERE'S MY COUNTEROFFER.

10:51.385 --> 10:52.986
EAT MY BALLS.

10:53.020 --> 10:54.488
UH, SORRY, WIZARD.

10:54.521 --> 10:55.722
Shut up.

10:55.756 --> 10:57.991
SILAS, IF YOU CAN'T TAKE THE
STRESS OF TOUGH NEGOTIATIONS ‐‐

10:58.025 --> 10:59.126
DID YOU HIT "SAVE"
FIRST?

10:59.159 --> 11:00.861
THAT'S A VERY UNSTABLE
OPERATING SYSTEM.

11:00.894 --> 11:02.996
WE'RE DONE HERE.
OH, PLEASE.

11:03.030 --> 11:04.064
[ BUZZER ]

11:04.097 --> 11:05.532
[ DOOR OPENS ]

11:13.207 --> 11:15.909
YOU SAY YOU VALIDATE?

11:15.943 --> 11:18.478
[ SIGHS ]

11:23.684 --> 11:25.652
[ SIGHS ]

11:32.492 --> 11:35.028
DEAD MEXICAN!

11:35.062 --> 11:38.432
DEAD MEXICAN. DEAD MEXICAN.

11:38.465 --> 11:40.501
DEAD MEXICAN.

11:41.602 --> 11:44.505
DEAD MEXICAN!

11:44.538 --> 11:47.407
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

11:58.652 --> 12:01.388
[ Dialing, ringing ]

12:01.421 --> 12:03.257
HEY. IT'S ME.

12:03.290 --> 12:08.128
UH, STILL ‐‐ STILL WEIGHING
THE WHOLE MOVING‐IN THING.

12:08.161 --> 12:10.664
BUT GUESS
WHO I RAN INTO.

12:10.697 --> 12:12.900
OUR OLD FRIEND SUCIO.

12:12.933 --> 12:16.303
HE'S LOOKING
A...LITTLE STIFF.

12:16.336 --> 12:20.941
SO, IF YOU COULD SEND SOMEONE
TO PICK HIM UP ‐‐ SOON.

12:20.974 --> 12:23.944
HE'S HANGING OUT
IN THE GARAGE.

12:23.977 --> 12:25.279
OKAY, BYE.

12:25.312 --> 12:27.948
[ SIGHS ]

12:27.981 --> 12:30.484
KEEP HIM COMPANY.

12:30.517 --> 12:32.252
[ SIGHS LIGHTLY ]

12:32.286 --> 12:35.455
I DIDN'T REALIZE WE WERE GOING
FULL PERIOD WITH THIS THING.

12:35.489 --> 12:38.859
I WOULD'VE ‐‐ I WOULD'VE WORN
MY LOVERBOY HEADBAND.

12:38.892 --> 12:40.093
I LOOK RIDICULOUS.

12:40.127 --> 12:42.663
I KNEW IT,
BUT MY GUILD ENCOURAGED ME.

12:42.696 --> 12:44.998
NO, MAGS, YOU LOOK AM‐‐

12:45.032 --> 12:46.533
YOUR GUILD?

12:46.567 --> 12:47.634
ONLINE‐GAMING WORLD?

12:47.668 --> 12:48.635
MM‐HMM.
I'M A MAGE.

12:48.669 --> 12:49.636
MM‐HMM.

12:49.670 --> 12:50.671
AND, BELIEVE IT OR NOT,

12:50.704 --> 12:52.639
I'M ACTUALLY PRETTY OUTGOING
AND POPULAR THERE.

12:52.673 --> 12:54.541
POPULAR IN THE GAME
AS A MAGE?

12:54.575 --> 12:57.110
OH, YEAH. MY SPELL‐HIT RATIO
IS, LIKE, OFF THE CHARTS.

12:57.144 --> 12:58.612
[ CHUCKLES, SIGHS ]

12:58.645 --> 13:00.981
YOU ‐‐ YOU THINK
I'M PATHETIC.

13:01.014 --> 13:03.383
I'M DRESSED
LIKE MOLLY RINGWALD.

13:03.417 --> 13:06.854
I'M SORRY. I‐I HAVE
THIS FIERCE IMAGINATION.

13:06.887 --> 13:08.021
I ALWAYS HAVE.

13:08.055 --> 13:10.357
NO, IT'S ADMIRABLE,
ACTUALLY.

13:10.390 --> 13:13.393
I CAN'T REMEMBER THE LAST TIME
I IMAGINED ANYTHING.

13:13.427 --> 13:15.896
THAT IS SO SAD.

13:15.929 --> 13:18.899
SO [SIGHS] FONDUE.

13:18.932 --> 13:20.501
THIS IS WHERE WE WENT
ON OUR DATE.

13:20.534 --> 13:21.602
TOTALLY EXCITING.

13:21.635 --> 13:25.272
I HAPPEN TO LOVE DIPPING THINGS
INTO OTHER THINGS.

13:25.305 --> 13:28.075
WELL, THE FUN IS THAT YOU GET
TO COOK THE MEAT YOURSELF.

13:28.108 --> 13:29.510
THAT'S WHAT JUDAH SAID.

13:29.543 --> 13:31.178
WHAT YOU SAID.

13:31.211 --> 13:35.215
WHAT I SA‐‐ YES.
WHAT I SAID ‐‐ ME, JUDAH.

13:35.249 --> 13:37.518
[ Deep voice ]
YOU COOK IT YOURSELF.

13:37.551 --> 13:41.021
[ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH.

13:41.054 --> 13:44.925
SO, UM, WHAT MADE YOU
FINALLY ASK ME OUT?

13:44.958 --> 13:48.295
I MEAN,
YOU'RE SUCH A STUD‐MUFFIN.

13:48.328 --> 13:50.964
I GUESS WHEN I SAW YOU
AT THE...

13:50.998 --> 13:53.300
AT THE FOOD COURT. I‐I WORKED
AT HOT DOG ON A STICK.

13:53.333 --> 13:55.335
THE WAY THAT YOU
HANDLED THE BATTER...

13:55.369 --> 13:56.470
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:56.503 --> 13:59.439
I SAW YOU, AND I FIGURED
I'M JUST HERE FOR THE SUMMER

13:59.473 --> 14:03.877
AND LIFE IS SHORT
AND PEOPLE ARE SUCH PHONIES.

14:03.911 --> 14:06.079
LIKE J. D. SALINGER SAID.

14:06.113 --> 14:09.216
OH, MY GOD,
YOU ALWAYS QUOTED THAT.

14:09.249 --> 14:11.018
[ Normal voice ]
THAT'S RIGHT.

14:11.051 --> 14:12.753
JUDAH READ THAT BOOK
EVERY SUMMER.

14:12.786 --> 14:13.887
[ Deep voice ] PHONIES.

14:13.921 --> 14:16.256
GODDAMN PHONIES.

14:16.290 --> 14:18.525
BUT YOU'RE NOT A PHONY,
MAGS.

14:18.559 --> 14:21.695
YOU'RE REAL.

14:21.728 --> 14:23.564
AND I'M REAL.

14:23.597 --> 14:24.831
ME ‐‐ JUDAH.

14:24.865 --> 14:26.300
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:26.333 --> 14:29.469
SO...LET'S BE REAL
TOGETHER.

14:31.338 --> 14:33.907
I WANT YOU
TO TAKE MY VIRGINITY.

14:33.941 --> 14:36.510
[ SPITS ]

14:36.543 --> 14:39.246
[ CHIMES JINGLE ]

14:52.526 --> 14:57.197
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

14:57.231 --> 15:00.100
[ THEREMIN SQUEALING ]

15:07.875 --> 15:09.643
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?

15:09.676 --> 15:10.844
HI, ISABEL.

15:10.878 --> 15:12.045
IT'S A THEREMIN.

15:12.079 --> 15:14.515
IT'S ONE OF THE EARLIEST
ELECTRONIC INSTRUMENTS.

15:14.548 --> 15:15.315
SUPER.

15:15.349 --> 15:17.117
WHAT'S IT DOING
IN MY HOUSE?

15:17.150 --> 15:19.253
WE FOUND IT ‐‐
BY A DUMPSTER.

15:19.286 --> 15:20.454
YOU DON'T HAVE TO LIE
TO HER.

15:20.487 --> 15:22.856
I WAS SELLING
SILAS' LEFTOVER CHEESE‐POT,

15:22.890 --> 15:25.526
AND MY SHITBALL TEACHER
JACKED MY STASH.

15:25.559 --> 15:26.460
SO I JACKED HIM BACK.

15:27.561 --> 15:29.263
IGNACIO HELPED US.

15:29.296 --> 15:32.032
[ MUSIC PLAYING ON HEADPHONES ]

15:32.065 --> 15:34.501
YOU HELPED SHANE
ROB HIS TEACHER?

15:34.535 --> 15:35.736
YOU'RE WELCOME.

15:35.769 --> 15:36.737
[ SCOFFS ]

15:36.770 --> 15:38.238
I CAN'T LIVE LIKE THIS
ANYMORE.

15:38.272 --> 15:40.440
WHAT HAVE I ALLOWED
IN MY HOUSE?

15:40.474 --> 15:44.144
SHANE WAS A GOOD KID.
NOW HE'S ROBBING HIS TEACHER.

15:44.178 --> 15:45.879
[ MUSIC TURNS OFF ]

15:45.913 --> 15:48.882
I AM SO SORRY
THAT I EXPOSED HIM

15:48.916 --> 15:51.518
TO THE WORLD
OF CRIMINAL ACTIVITIES...

15:51.552 --> 15:53.554
FOR THE FIRST TIME.

16:05.632 --> 16:07.301
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:11.104 --> 16:13.473
HEY, SILAS!
COME HERE. LOOK AT THIS.

16:17.411 --> 16:20.814
HUH? A SELF‐PORTRAIT
FROM MY BLUE‐BALLS PERIOD.

16:20.848 --> 16:23.817
EVER GET TIRED
OF BEING A COMPLETE JOKE?

16:23.851 --> 16:24.818
WHAT?

16:24.852 --> 16:28.288
I'M DELIGHTFUL.
PEOPLE LOVE ME.

16:28.322 --> 16:30.157
NOT TO BE IN BUSINESS WITH YOU,
THEY DON'T.

16:30.190 --> 16:32.159
HEY, I WAS
A WELL‐RESPECTED C. P. A.

16:32.192 --> 16:34.428
NOTICE THE USE
OF THE PAST TENSE?

16:34.461 --> 16:38.198
YOU HURTFUL,
TOOTHY LITTLE SHIT.

16:38.232 --> 16:39.032
TEEFY!

16:39.066 --> 16:40.701
MAN BOOBS.

16:40.734 --> 16:41.869
NO, YOU DON'T
MAKE UP THE NAMES.

16:41.902 --> 16:43.136
THAT'S MY THING,
GOLDILOCKS.

16:43.170 --> 16:45.806
NO, I CAN DO BETTER ‐‐
MORMON‐FACE!

16:45.839 --> 16:48.675
GIGANTOR. EMBEZZLER.

16:48.709 --> 16:50.010
GIRLFRIEND‐DEPORTER.

16:50.043 --> 16:52.813
STOP IT, DEAF‐GIRL FUCKER!
DEAF‐FUCKER!

16:52.846 --> 16:54.548
BAD DAD. ABANDONER!

16:54.581 --> 16:56.450
ORPHAN. FATHER‐KILLER!

16:57.484 --> 17:00.320
AAH!

17:07.828 --> 17:09.630
I'M SORRY, DOUG.

17:09.663 --> 17:12.833
NO, I'M SORRY.

17:12.866 --> 17:14.535
I JUST SAY THINGS.

17:14.568 --> 17:17.671
SOMETIMES ‐‐
SOMETIMES I ACTUALLY THINK

17:17.704 --> 17:20.674
I'M SLIGHTLY RETARDED
IN THE MOUTH.

17:20.707 --> 17:22.709
AND YOU DIDN'T
KILL YOUR FATHER.

17:22.743 --> 17:25.746
SHANE DID.

17:26.747 --> 17:28.282
I'LL, UH...

17:28.315 --> 17:30.350
SO, I...

17:30.384 --> 17:31.451
YEAH.
YEAH.

17:33.453 --> 17:34.521
YEAH.
OKAY.

17:34.555 --> 17:36.623
[ DOOR OPENS ]

17:36.657 --> 17:38.225
OOH, OOH.

17:39.326 --> 17:40.827
OH!

17:40.861 --> 17:42.763
HOLA.

17:42.796 --> 17:45.032
MI NOMBRE ES CELIA.

17:45.065 --> 17:47.201
THE BODY IS WHERE?

17:47.234 --> 17:48.702
MM.

17:55.742 --> 17:57.578
UGH.

18:02.783 --> 18:05.285
SO, WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO,
EXACTLY?

18:06.753 --> 18:08.388
IS THAT ACID?

18:08.422 --> 18:10.691
DO YOU HAVE TO CUT HIM UP
INTO LITTLE PIECES BEFORE?

18:10.724 --> 18:14.494
LADY LEAVES NOW, GOES GETS
A FALAFEL OR SOMETHING.

18:14.528 --> 18:16.763
I DON'T REALLY HAVE
ANYWHERE TO GO.

18:16.797 --> 18:19.399
I'M SORT OF BETWEEN THINGS
RIGHT NOW,

18:19.433 --> 18:22.936
FRESH FROM A SPELL WITH SOME
REVOLUTIONARIES IN YOUR COUNTRY.

18:22.970 --> 18:24.872
RODOLFO.
YOU KNOW HIM?

18:24.905 --> 18:27.040
PIERCING EYES,
TOTAL VAGINA.

18:27.074 --> 18:30.344
YOU KNOW, NANCY'S TOSSING ME OUT
ON MY ASS.

18:30.377 --> 18:33.947
SEE, AND I FINALLY UNDERSTAND
WHAT RODOLFO MEANT

18:33.981 --> 18:36.483
WHEN HE BABBLED ON
ABOUT THE POWERLESS

18:36.517 --> 18:39.720
NEEDING TO USE THEIR WEAKNESS
AS AN ADVANTAGE.

18:39.753 --> 18:42.956
I JUST WISH THAT I HAD SOMETHING
THAT I COULD USE ‐‐

18:42.990 --> 18:46.627
[ SIGHS ]

18:46.660 --> 18:49.029
WE WERE RIGHT HERE.

18:49.062 --> 18:51.832
IT WAS SO ROMANTIC.

18:51.865 --> 18:52.699
HERE?

18:52.733 --> 18:54.034
UH‐HUH.

18:54.067 --> 18:56.570
[ BOTTLE ROLLS ]

18:56.603 --> 18:58.272
GIVE ME YOUR JACKET.

19:00.774 --> 19:03.410
[ GRUNTS ]

19:07.181 --> 19:10.617
YOU WERE TALKING ABOUT
HOW LAME "FOOTLOOSE" WAS,

19:10.651 --> 19:14.755
AND I KEPT THINKING,
"WHEN IS HE GONNA JUMP ME?"

19:14.788 --> 19:15.789
OH, I LOVED "FOOTLOOSE."

19:15.822 --> 19:17.658
THAT'S JUDAH'S
GAY BROTHER TALKING.

19:17.691 --> 19:18.659
I MEAN, PFFT.

19:18.692 --> 19:21.562
[ Deep voice ] QUEER BAIT ‐‐
ALL THE DANCING.

19:21.595 --> 19:23.497
HOMO‐CITY.

19:23.530 --> 19:27.000
OH! OH, JUDAH,
YOU'RE SO FUCKING BOSS!

19:27.034 --> 19:30.938
MM‐HMM!
OH, JUDAH,
STICK IT IN ME!

19:30.971 --> 19:32.806
[ Normal voice ] WOW.
YOU REALLY JUST SAID THAT.

19:32.840 --> 19:35.042
JUDAH, BORK ME
WITH YOUR HOT TOOL!

19:35.075 --> 19:37.644
AND YOU SAID THAT, TOO.
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:37.678 --> 19:39.046
[ COUGHS ]

19:39.079 --> 19:40.981
I‐IS ANYTHING WRONG?

19:41.014 --> 19:41.982
SHOULD I SUCK YOU?

19:42.015 --> 19:43.550
OH, NO, NO, NO,
THAT'S ‐‐

19:43.584 --> 19:44.818
I MEAN, THAT'S NOT ‐‐

19:44.852 --> 19:46.320
[ Deep voice ]
THAT'S NOT WHAT WE DID.

19:46.353 --> 19:49.289
OH, YOU'RE RIGHT.
I‐I WAS LIKE THIS.

19:49.323 --> 19:51.358
COME ON, JUDAH.
MAKE ME A WOMAN.

19:51.391 --> 19:54.161
[ Normal voice ] UH,
MAYBE WE SHOULD SAVE OURSELVES.

19:54.194 --> 19:55.462
YOU WANT THAT MONEY
OR DON'T YOU?

19:55.495 --> 19:56.897
[ Deep voice ]
YOU KNOW WHAT I...WANT.

19:56.930 --> 19:58.732
JUDAH!

19:58.765 --> 20:02.469
Copenhagen. Copenhagen.

20:02.503 --> 20:06.406
Copenhagen. Copenhagen.

20:06.440 --> 20:07.841
Copenhagen.

20:07.875 --> 20:09.009
[ SIGHS ]

20:09.042 --> 20:11.011
[ Normal voice ] OH.

20:11.044 --> 20:13.480
WHAT DO YOU KNOW?
IMAGINATION.

20:16.116 --> 20:18.385
OKAY.
OH, JUDAH, YES.

20:18.418 --> 20:20.387
[ GRUNTING ]

20:20.420 --> 20:23.123
Oh, God.
Copenhagen, Copenhagen.

20:23.156 --> 20:25.325
OH, JUDAH, YES.
JUDAH, JUDAH, JUDAH!

20:25.359 --> 20:28.328
Copenhagen, Copenhagen,
Copenhagen...

20:28.362 --> 20:30.831
BORK ME! BORK ME!
BORK ME! BORK ME!

20:30.864 --> 20:32.366
[ COUGHS ]

20:32.399 --> 20:33.734
Copenhagen.

20:33.767 --> 20:35.035
[ FARTS ]

20:35.068 --> 20:37.104
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]
OH, JUDAH, YES.

20:37.137 --> 20:39.873
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

20:39.907 --> 20:41.675
[ SIGHS ]

20:45.078 --> 20:47.481
HI.
NANCY BOTWIN.

20:47.514 --> 20:49.149
I'M SHANE'S MOTHER.

20:49.183 --> 20:52.719
UM, COULD YOU...
PUT DOWN THE BAT?

20:54.621 --> 20:55.522
THANKS.

20:55.556 --> 20:59.760
WE BROUGHT BACK
YOUR INSTRUMENT THINGY.

20:59.793 --> 21:00.861
INTACT.

21:00.894 --> 21:04.932
AND, UM, A REPLACEMENT
ANIMAL COMPANION.

21:04.965 --> 21:08.035
IT'S AN IGUANA.
THEY EAT GREENS AND FRUITS.

21:08.068 --> 21:09.236
BIRDS CARRY GERMS.

21:09.269 --> 21:11.605
IT'S A MAJOR TURN‐OFF
FOR THE LADIES.

21:11.638 --> 21:15.676
I BROUGHT BACK
YOUR ROLLER SKATES, SUNGLASSES.

21:15.709 --> 21:18.579
I'M GONNA HAVE TO GIVE YOU
AN I. O. U. ON THE VIDEO THING.

21:18.612 --> 21:19.713
ANYWAY, SHANE?

21:19.746 --> 21:22.349
I'M SORRY
I KILLED YOUR COCKATOO.

21:22.382 --> 21:26.019
HE WAS AN INNOCENT CASUALTY
OF YOUTHFUL VENGEANCE.

21:26.053 --> 21:28.155
HE TAUGHT ME
A VALUABLE LESSON

21:28.188 --> 21:30.858
ABOUT THE DESTRUCTIVE POWER
OF FIREARMS?

21:30.891 --> 21:35.062
SO HIS DEATH
WAS NOT IN VAIN.

21:35.095 --> 21:37.731
YOU'RE GETTING AN "F."
NOW GET THE FUCK OUT.

21:37.764 --> 21:40.067
OKAY,
THAT WASN'T NECESSARY.

21:40.100 --> 21:42.169
YOU KILLED SEACREST.
AND HE APOLOGIZED.

21:42.202 --> 21:44.104
GET THE FUCK
OUT OF MY APARTMENT!

21:44.137 --> 21:46.473
OH, THAT WAS DUMB.
THAT WAS REALLY DUMB.

21:46.507 --> 21:47.774
WHAT THE FUCK ‐‐
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

21:47.808 --> 21:49.676
MOM?

21:49.710 --> 21:52.813
STEALING FROM STUDENTS
IS A NO‐NO.

21:52.846 --> 21:54.214
IT'S UNSEEMLY,

21:54.248 --> 21:56.517
NOT TO MENTION
GROSS ABUSE OF YOUR POSITION.

21:56.550 --> 21:59.019
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA
DO IT AGAIN, ARE YOU?

21:59.052 --> 22:00.654
[ Strained ]
I WON'T. I'M SORRY.

22:00.687 --> 22:01.755
CAN I KICK HIM?
NO, SWEETIE.

22:01.788 --> 22:03.257
BY THE WAY,
YOU'RE GROUNDED ‐‐

22:03.290 --> 22:06.460
NO VIDEO GAMES, NO...TWEETERING,
NOTHING ELECTRONIC.

22:06.493 --> 22:07.594
IT'S DESENSITIZING.

22:07.628 --> 22:10.664
PUTS YOU OUT OF TOUCH
WITH YOUR HUMANITY.

22:10.697 --> 22:12.399
YOU CAN'T AFFORD THAT.

22:12.432 --> 22:14.001
[ GASPS ]

22:15.469 --> 22:18.939
REMEMBER ‐‐ FRUITS AND GREENS.
TAKE CARE OF HIM.

22:18.972 --> 22:22.009
THIS COULD BE
A WHOLE NEW START FOR YOU.

22:27.514 --> 22:30.184
I'M GOING INTO YOUR HOUSE
TO TAKE A BATH.

22:30.217 --> 22:32.819
TRY IT, AND THE TOASTER
GOES IN WITH YOU.

22:32.853 --> 22:36.490
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHAT I DID TONIGHT?

22:36.523 --> 22:41.128
I WATCHED A DEAD BODY GET
REMOVED FROM YOUR OLD COLDSPOT

22:41.161 --> 22:44.131
AND SEALED
INTO A BARREL OF ACID.

22:44.164 --> 22:47.634
DO YOU KNOW,
THOSE GUYS WERE SO SWEET.

22:47.668 --> 22:51.972
THEY EVEN LET ME TAKE SOME
CHOICE PHOTOS BEFORE THEY LEFT.

22:52.005 --> 22:54.975
LOOK ‐‐
IT'S NANCY'S HOUSE.

22:55.008 --> 22:58.412
SO, YES, I THINK THAT I WILL BE
TAKING THAT BATH,

22:58.445 --> 23:02.182
AND, ALSO, I THINK
I'LL BE LIVING IN THAT GARAGE

23:02.216 --> 23:03.951
FOR AS LONG AS I WANT.

23:03.984 --> 23:06.787
OH, AND I'LL NEED SOME CASH
TO FIX THE PLACE UP.

23:06.820 --> 23:09.590
I HEAR
IKEA'S HAVING A TENT SALE.

23:09.623 --> 23:13.594
SELFISH PREGNANT CUNT.

23:13.627 --> 23:15.295
GOOD NIGHT.

23:20.634 --> 23:22.636
[ CHIMES JINGLE ]

23:26.907 --> 23:28.842
THEY'RE DEAD.

23:28.876 --> 23:30.711
ALL DEAD.

23:30.744 --> 23:32.679
[ SCOFFS ]

23:32.713 --> 23:34.414
SNUFFED OUT!

23:34.448 --> 23:36.016
BUNNIES.

23:36.049 --> 23:38.685
AH, SLUGS.

23:38.719 --> 23:40.587
LITTLE BLACK
FUCKING SLUGS!

23:42.589 --> 23:43.757
THEY'RE EVERYWHERE.

23:43.790 --> 23:45.993
IT'S AN INSIDE JOB.

23:48.161 --> 23:49.296
I PUT BARRIERS UP.

23:49.329 --> 23:52.699
THEY JUST...
SLIPPED RIGHT THROUGH.

23:52.733 --> 23:54.401
I GOT THE MONEY.

23:54.434 --> 23:56.236
THERE'S A LOT.

23:56.270 --> 23:57.037
WHAT? HOW?

23:57.070 --> 23:58.739
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

23:58.772 --> 23:59.907
IT JUST...

23:59.940 --> 24:03.010
I NEED A SHOWER.
I NEED TO BE SANDBLASTED.

24:03.043 --> 24:04.178
I NEED A HUG.

24:04.211 --> 24:06.046
THE POINT IS, I HAVE IT.

24:08.482 --> 24:12.286
I'M NOT SURE WHAT
I'M SUPPOSED TO DO, ANDY.

24:12.319 --> 24:15.622
IT ISN'T SAFE HERE
ANYMORE.

24:15.656 --> 24:17.424
IT'S ALL WRONG.

24:17.457 --> 24:18.892
[ SIGHS ]

24:18.926 --> 24:20.827
YOU KNOW CELIA'S
LIVING IN THE GARAGE?

24:20.861 --> 24:21.828
YES.

24:21.862 --> 24:23.263
WE HAD
A NICE LONG CONVERSATION

24:23.297 --> 24:25.465
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN FLESH HITS ACID.

24:25.499 --> 24:26.600
[ SIGHS ]

24:26.633 --> 24:29.703
WHY IS FUCKING ARMAGEDDON
ALWAYS COMING DOWN ON ME?

24:29.736 --> 24:30.871
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:30.904 --> 24:31.872
YOU DO IT.

24:31.905 --> 24:34.741
YOU DO KNOW THAT.

24:34.775 --> 24:37.377
YOU HAVE TO KNOW
THAT IT'S ALL YOU.

24:45.552 --> 24:48.989
[ SNIFFLES ]

24:53.093 --> 24:54.828
FORGET VAN NUYS.

24:54.862 --> 24:56.063
KEEP THE BABY.

24:56.096 --> 24:57.998
IT DOES NOT MATTER.

24:58.031 --> 24:59.600
BUT WE LEAVE.

24:59.633 --> 25:00.634
SHANE DID SOMETHING
SO ‐‐

25:00.667 --> 25:02.970
THAT'S WHY WE HAVE TO GO.
IT'S NOT SAFE HERE.

25:03.003 --> 25:04.338
EVEN YOUR PLANTS.

25:04.371 --> 25:05.405
BUT ESTEBAN ‐‐

25:05.439 --> 25:06.440
LEAVE HIM A NOTE.

25:06.473 --> 25:07.341
A NOTE?!

25:07.374 --> 25:09.109
WRITE HIM A NOTE,
LIKE THE OLDEN TIMES.

25:09.142 --> 25:11.144
BREAK HIS HEART IN INK.

25:11.178 --> 25:14.314
HE WILL UNDERSTAND
IF HE LOVES YOU.

25:14.348 --> 25:16.583
I DO HAVE
NICE HANDWRITING.

25:16.617 --> 25:18.385
AND IN THE MORNING,
WE GO.

25:18.418 --> 25:20.721
I'LL THROW SOME AMBIEN
IN IGNACIO'S SMOOTHIE,

25:20.754 --> 25:23.790
